• copy drafts/new to drafts/NAME
• edit drafts/NAME/index.html
• replace TITLE with the real title
• write the post (this may take multiple days)
• replace DATE with publication date
• create YYYY/MM/DD/ directories
• move drafts/NAME to YYYY/MM/DD/
• replace URL with YYYY/MM/DD/NAME/
• add to index.html
• run Makefile
